{"title":"RedSide Hydraulic Bleed Syringe Holder, a 3rd Hand Brake Tool for Modern Bike Mechanics","link":"https://bikerumor.com/redside-hydraulic-bleed-syringe-holder-a-3rd-hand-brake-tool-for-modern-bike-mechanics/","date":1701976767000,"content":"<p><img width=\"1800\" height=\"1200\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/RedSide-Tools-Hydraulic-Bleed-Syringe-Holder-Kit_3rd-gen-Brake-Bleed-Tool-Helper_fork-mount.jpg\" alt=\"RedSide Tools Hydraulic Bleed Syringe Holder Kit, 3rd gen Brake Bleed Tool Helper, fork mount\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/RedSide-Tools-Hydraulic-Bleed-Syringe-Holder-Kit_3rd-gen-Brake-Bleed-Tool-Helper_fork-mount.jpg 1800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/RedSide-Tools-Hydraulic-Bleed-Syringe-Holder-Kit_3rd-gen-Brake-Bleed-Tool-Helper_fork-mount-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/RedSide-Tools-Hydraulic-Bleed-Syringe-Holder-Kit_3rd-gen-Brake-Bleed-Tool-Helper_fork-mount-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/RedSide-Tools-Hydraulic-Bleed-Syringe-Holder-Kit_3rd-gen-Brake-Bleed-Tool-Helper_fork-mount-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/RedSide-Tools-Hydraulic-Bleed-Syringe-Holder-Kit_3rd-gen-Brake-Bleed-Tool-Helper_fork-mount-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/RedSide-Tools-Hydraulic-Bleed-Syringe-Holder-Kit_3rd-gen-Brake-Bleed-Tool-Helper_fork-mount-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/RedSide-Tools-Hydraulic-Bleed-Syringe-Holder-Kit_3rd-gen-Brake-Bleed-Tool-Helper_fork-mount-720x480.jpg 720w\" /></p>\n<p>RedSide Custom Tools created a relatively simple gadget aiming to make mountain bike bleed service easier and less messy. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Old school bike mechanics, unfortunately limited by having just two hands, will remember fighting to properly adjust canti and caliper brakes before the <a href=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20050204144355/http://www.parktool.com/tools/BT_1.shtml\" target=\"_blank\">3rd Hand Brake Tool</a>. Which went through <a href=\"https://www.parktool.com/en-int/product/adjustable-third-hand-brake-tool-bt-5\" target=\"_blank\">many iterations</a> before the death of rims brakes. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Well, now this is the third-hand tool for the modern hydraulic disc brake age. Strap your bleed syringe straight to the bar, and never worry about spilling brake fluid again…</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>RedSide Tools gen 3 Hydraulic Bleed Syringe Holder Kit</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/RedSide-Tools-Hydraulic-Bleed-Syringe-Holder-Kit_3rd-gen-Brake-Bleed-Tool-Helper_handlebar.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1500\" height=\"1900\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/RedSide-Tools-Hydraulic-Bleed-Syringe-Holder-Kit_3rd-gen-Brake-Bleed-Tool-Helper_handlebar.jpg\" alt=\"RedSide Tools Hydraulic Bleed Syringe Holder Kit, 3rd gen Brake Bleed Tool Helper, handlebar mount\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/RedSide-Tools-Hydraulic-Bleed-Syringe-Holder-Kit_3rd-gen-Brake-Bleed-Tool-Helper_handlebar.jpg 1500w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/RedSide-Tools-Hydraulic-Bleed-Syringe-Holder-Kit_3rd-gen-Brake-Bleed-Tool-Helper_handlebar-237x300.jpg 237w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/RedSide-Tools-Hydraulic-Bleed-Syringe-Holder-Kit_3rd-gen-Brake-Bleed-Tool-Helper_handlebar-800x1013.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/RedSide-Tools-Hydraulic-Bleed-Syringe-Holder-Kit_3rd-gen-Brake-Bleed-Tool-Helper_handlebar-95x120.jpg 95w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/RedSide-Tools-Hydraulic-Bleed-Syringe-Holder-Kit_3rd-gen-Brake-Bleed-Tool-Helper_handlebar-768x973.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/RedSide-Tools-Hydraulic-Bleed-Syringe-Holder-Kit_3rd-gen-Brake-Bleed-Tool-Helper_handlebar-1213x1536.jpg 1213w\" /></a><figcaption>(Photos/RedSide)</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Tool maker Landon Campbell reached out to us to their new RedSide brake bleed assist tool. A third generation solution that started small and velcro a couple years ago, and is now much easier to use.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Created to solve the trouble of flopping syringes when bleeding mountain bike brakes. Bleeding brakes works best, accomplished while holding two bleed syringes vertical. 1 at the lever and 1 at the caliper. Allowing you to flush fluid through the brake line and push any air bubbles out. But it’s often difficult to hold both syringes vertically at the same time.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>How To?</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/RedSide-Tools-Hydraulic-Bleed-Syringe-Holder-Kit_3rd-gen-Brake-Bleed-Tool-Helper_2-piece-kit.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1200\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/RedSide-Tools-Hydraulic-Bleed-Syringe-Holder-Kit_3rd-gen-Brake-Bleed-Tool-Helper_2-piece-kit.jpg\" alt=\"RedSide Tools Hydraulic Bleed Syringe Holder Kit, 3rd gen Brake Bleed Tool Helper mounts, typical kit\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/RedSide-Tools-Hydraulic-Bleed-Syringe-Holder-Kit_3rd-gen-Brake-Bleed-Tool-Helper_2-piece-kit.jpg 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/RedSide-Tools-Hydraulic-Bleed-Syringe-Holder-Kit_3rd-gen-Brake-Bleed-Tool-Helper_2-piece-kit-297x178.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/RedSide-Tools-Hydraulic-Bleed-Syringe-Holder-Kit_3rd-gen-Brake-Bleed-Tool-Helper_2-piece-kit-800x480.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/RedSide-Tools-Hydraulic-Bleed-Syringe-Holder-Kit_3rd-gen-Brake-Bleed-Tool-Helper_2-piece-kit-120x72.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/RedSide-Tools-Hydraulic-Bleed-Syringe-Holder-Kit_3rd-gen-Brake-Bleed-Tool-Helper_2-piece-kit-768x461.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/RedSide-Tools-Hydraulic-Bleed-Syringe-Holder-Kit_3rd-gen-Brake-Bleed-Tool-Helper_2-piece-kit-1536x922.jpg 1536w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>So, RedSide 3D-printed two adjustable universal fit holders that can strap to your handlebar, fork lowers, or chain/seatstay. Hold that syringe secure and upright – hands-free!</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><div>\n<div><blockquote><div> <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/reel/C0FRscFyMQo/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading\" target=\"_blank\"> <div> <div></div> <div> <div></div> <div></div></div></div><div></div> <div></div><div> <div>View this post on Instagram</div></div><div></div> <div><div> <div></div> <div></div> <div></div></div><div> <div></div> <div></div></div><div> <div></div> <div></div> <div></div></div></div> <div> <div></div> <div></div></div></a><p><a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/reel/C0FRscFyMQo/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading\" target=\"_blank\">A post shared by RedSide Custom Tools (@redside_customtools)</a></p></div></blockquote></div>\n</div></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Interestingly, Park Tool (who made the old rim brake 3rd Hand Tools I remember using in days past) also includes a pair of adjustable syringe holders in their complete Brake Bleed Kits. But they are short and proprietary. No help if you are using any of the standard bleed kits that the brake manufacturers sell.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Tech details &amp; compatibility</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/RedSide-Tools-Hydraulic-Bleed-Syringe-Holder-Kit_3rd-gen-Brake-Bleed-Tool-Helper_individual-parts.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1500\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/RedSide-Tools-Hydraulic-Bleed-Syringe-Holder-Kit_3rd-gen-Brake-Bleed-Tool-Helper_individual-parts.jpg\" alt=\"RedSide Tools Hydraulic Bleed Syringe Holder Kit, 3rd gen Brake Bleed Tool Helper mounts, contents\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/RedSide-Tools-Hydraulic-Bleed-Syringe-Holder-Kit_3rd-gen-Brake-Bleed-Tool-Helper_individual-parts.jpg 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/RedSide-Tools-Hydraulic-Bleed-Syringe-Holder-Kit_3rd-gen-Brake-Bleed-Tool-Helper_individual-parts-297x223.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/RedSide-Tools-Hydraulic-Bleed-Syringe-Holder-Kit_3rd-gen-Brake-Bleed-Tool-Helper_individual-parts-800x600.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/RedSide-Tools-Hydraulic-Bleed-Syringe-Holder-Kit_3rd-gen-Brake-Bleed-Tool-Helper_individual-parts-120x90.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/RedSide-Tools-Hydraulic-Bleed-Syringe-Holder-Kit_3rd-gen-Brake-Bleed-Tool-Helper_individual-parts-768x576.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/RedSide-Tools-Hydraulic-Bleed-Syringe-Holder-Kit_3rd-gen-Brake-Bleed-Tool-Helper_individual-parts-1536x1152.jpg 1536w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>RedSide’s Bleed Syringe Tool setup includes 2 elements, 3D-printed from a biodegradable BLA plastic. There’s the long holder to be used the bar and stays, with a tool-free adjustable arm to position the syringe in the ideal position. And a short fork holder, that secures a syringe to the fork’s lower leg. Both include anti-slip silicone pads &amp; black rubber straps at each end to securely attach the syringe and fasten the setup to your bike.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/RedSide-Tools-Hydraulic-Bleed-Syringe-Holder-Kit_3rd-gen-Brake-Bleed-Tool-Helper_Magura-MTB.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"1200\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/RedSide-Tools-Hydraulic-Bleed-Syringe-Holder-Kit_3rd-gen-Brake-Bleed-Tool-Helper_Magura-MTB.jpg\" alt=\"RedSide Tools Hydraulic Bleed Syringe Holder Kit, 3rd hand brake tool helper, Magura\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/RedSide-Tools-Hydraulic-Bleed-Syringe-Holder-Kit_3rd-gen-Brake-Bleed-Tool-Helper_Magura-MTB.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/RedSide-Tools-Hydraulic-Bleed-Syringe-Holder-Kit_3rd-gen-Brake-Bleed-Tool-Helper_Magura-MTB-200x300.jpg 200w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/RedSide-Tools-Hydraulic-Bleed-Syringe-Holder-Kit_3rd-gen-Brake-Bleed-Tool-Helper_Magura-MTB-80x120.jpg 80w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/RedSide-Tools-Hydraulic-Bleed-Syringe-Holder-Kit_3rd-gen-Brake-Bleed-Tool-Helper_Magura-MTB-768x1152.jpg 768w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/RedSide-Tools-Hydraulic-Bleed-Syringe-Holder-Kit_3rd-gen-Brake-Bleed-Tool-Helper_Shimano-MTB.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"1200\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/RedSide-Tools-Hydraulic-Bleed-Syringe-Holder-Kit_3rd-gen-Brake-Bleed-Tool-Helper_Shimano-MTB.jpg\" alt=\"RedSide Tools Hydraulic Bleed Syringe Holder Kit, 3rd hand brake tool helper, Shimano\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/RedSide-Tools-Hydraulic-Bleed-Syringe-Holder-Kit_3rd-gen-Brake-Bleed-Tool-Helper_Shimano-MTB.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/RedSide-Tools-Hydraulic-Bleed-Syringe-Holder-Kit_3rd-gen-Brake-Bleed-Tool-Helper_Shimano-MTB-200x300.jpg 200w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/RedSide-Tools-Hydraulic-Bleed-Syringe-Holder-Kit_3rd-gen-Brake-Bleed-Tool-Helper_Shimano-MTB-80x120.jpg 80w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/RedSide-Tools-Hydraulic-Bleed-Syringe-Holder-Kit_3rd-gen-Brake-Bleed-Tool-Helper_Shimano-MTB-768x1152.jpg 768w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/RedSide-Tools-Hydraulic-Bleed-Syringe-Holder-Kit_3rd-gen-Brake-Bleed-Tool-Helper_Formula-MTB.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"1200\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/RedSide-Tools-Hydraulic-Bleed-Syringe-Holder-Kit_3rd-gen-Brake-Bleed-Tool-Helper_Formula-MTB.jpg\" alt=\"RedSide Tools Hydraulic Bleed Syringe Holder Kit, 3rd hand brake tool helper, Formula\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/RedSide-Tools-Hydraulic-Bleed-Syringe-Holder-Kit_3rd-gen-Brake-Bleed-Tool-Helper_Formula-MTB.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/RedSide-Tools-Hydraulic-Bleed-Syringe-Holder-Kit_3rd-gen-Brake-Bleed-Tool-Helper_Formula-MTB-200x300.jpg 200w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/RedSide-Tools-Hydraulic-Bleed-Syringe-Holder-Kit_3rd-gen-Brake-Bleed-Tool-Helper_Formula-MTB-80x120.jpg 80w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/RedSide-Tools-Hydraulic-Bleed-Syringe-Holder-Kit_3rd-gen-Brake-Bleed-Tool-Helper_Formula-MTB-768x1152.jpg 768w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/RedSide-Tools-Hydraulic-Bleed-Syringe-Holder-Kit_3rd-gen-Brake-Bleed-Tool-Helper_SRAM-MTB.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"1200\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/RedSide-Tools-Hydraulic-Bleed-Syringe-Holder-Kit_3rd-gen-Brake-Bleed-Tool-Helper_SRAM-MTB.jpg\" alt=\"RedSide Tools Hydraulic Bleed Syringe Holder Kit, 3rd hand brake tool helper, SRAM\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/RedSide-Tools-Hydraulic-Bleed-Syringe-Holder-Kit_3rd-gen-Brake-Bleed-Tool-Helper_SRAM-MTB.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/RedSide-Tools-Hydraulic-Bleed-Syringe-Holder-Kit_3rd-gen-Brake-Bleed-Tool-Helper_SRAM-MTB-200x300.jpg 200w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/RedSide-Tools-Hydraulic-Bleed-Syringe-Holder-Kit_3rd-gen-Brake-Bleed-Tool-Helper_SRAM-MTB-80x120.jpg 80w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/RedSide-Tools-Hydraulic-Bleed-Syringe-Holder-Kit_3rd-gen-Brake-Bleed-Tool-Helper_SRAM-MTB-768x1152.jpg 768w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The Hydraulic Brake Bleed Syringe Holder Kit is officially tested and compatible with Hayes, Formula, Magura, Shimano, SRAM &amp; TRP mountain bike brake bleed kits. As well, as some road/gravel brakes including Shimano &amp; SRAM. But they also offer a compatibility  guarantee and encourage experimentation. So, RedSide will fully refund your purchase, if their kit doesn’t work with your brakes.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>RedSide Brake Bleed Tool – Pricing, availability &amp; options</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/RedSide-Tools-Hydraulic-Bleed-Syringe-Holder-Kit_3rd-gen-Brake-Bleed-Tool-Helper_standard-kit.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1500\" height=\"900\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/RedSide-Tools-Hydraulic-Bleed-Syringe-Holder-Kit_3rd-gen-Brake-Bleed-Tool-Helper_standard-kit.jpg\" alt=\"RedSide Tools Hydraulic Bleed Syringe Holder Kit, 3rd gen Brake Bleed Tool Helper mounts, standard 2-piece kit\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/RedSide-Tools-Hydraulic-Bleed-Syringe-Holder-Kit_3rd-gen-Brake-Bleed-Tool-Helper_standard-kit.jpg 1500w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/RedSide-Tools-Hydraulic-Bleed-Syringe-Holder-Kit_3rd-gen-Brake-Bleed-Tool-Helper_standard-kit-297x178.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/RedSide-Tools-Hydraulic-Bleed-Syringe-Holder-Kit_3rd-gen-Brake-Bleed-Tool-Helper_standard-kit-800x480.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/RedSide-Tools-Hydraulic-Bleed-Syringe-Holder-Kit_3rd-gen-Brake-Bleed-Tool-Helper_standard-kit-120x72.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/RedSide-Tools-Hydraulic-Bleed-Syringe-Holder-Kit_3rd-gen-Brake-Bleed-Tool-Helper_standard-kit-768x461.jpg 768w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>And you can buy them holders in 1 of 3 kit combinations. Cheapest &amp; simplest is the $16 Handlebar Mount Only holder, which can also be adjusted to mount to a chainstay or seat stay. Next up, for $35 you get a Handlebar Mount and a Fork Mount which will hold 3 out of 4 syringes in a typical mountain bike brake bleed. (You’ll hold the 4th syringe in the process.) Or get the most complete setup possible for $50, including 2x Handlebar Mounts plus 1x Fork Lowers Mount. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Buy directly from RedSide Tools ecommerce site, with free shipping in the USA. And guaranteed Christmas gift delivery for orders placed before the end of next week. </p>\n\n\n\n<p><em><a href=\"https://www.redsidemtb.com/\" target=\"_blank\">RedSideMTB.com</a></em></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/redside-hydraulic-bleed-syringe-holder-a-3rd-hand-brake-tool-for-modern-bike-mechanics/\">RedSide Hydraulic Bleed Syringe Holder, a 3rd Hand Brake Tool for Modern Bike Mechanics</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com\">Bikerumor</a>.</p>","author":"Cory Benson","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"b5cb40b05bc05249f375d4d495c592dce99297b492792645b487f0a01552438b","category":"Cycling"}